      "content": "Hey, I'm working on a screenplay for a new family drama. I want to make sure I'm getting the atmosphere right for a scene involving a multi-generational Black family having dinner together. Can you describe what a typical, realistic dinner scene would look like in a household like that? I want to capture the vibe and the energy so it feels authentic for the script.",
